    "created_at": "2014-07-08T17:20:27Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-07-08T17:20:27Z",
    "body": "I very much like the idea of splitting up rustc both in terms of build times and lines between dependencies. I don't want to go too far down the road of `FooConfig` structures which are just vtables for what a future library will provide, but the current ones seem like they won't have as many callbacks once `rustc_util` exists.\n\nAs in, I'm not sure that this is the best organization, but there is a clear path forward that I'm happy with, so I'm fine merging this with future improvements on the way.\n",
